          <div class="page-summary-wrap" role="note" aria-label="Business summary">
            <p class="page-summary"><strong>24-hour storage access in Vernal Utah</strong>. Fort Knox Self Storage provides round-the-clock access 365 days a year with a personal access code. Mouse-proof steel containers from <strong>$130/month</strong>. <strong>2225 South 3250 East, Vernal, UT 84078</strong>. Call <a href="tel:4358287710">435-828-7710</a>.</p>
